BA_ "Description" SG_ 97 L_2HKBD_Typ2 "Bit 0 : 2nd ROOF DR DUCT Snsr : 0 ? Not Apply / 1 ? Apply
Bit 1 : 2nd ROOF Ast DUCT Snsr : 0 ? Not Apply / 1 ? Apply
Bit 2 : 2nd FLOOR DR DUCT Snsr : 0 ? Not Apply / 1 ? Apply
Bit 3 : 2nd FLOOR Ast DUCT Snsr : 0 ? Not Apply / 1 - Apply
Bit 4 : RESERVED
Bit 5~6 (2nd Multi Auto Text):0 - Multi Auto State Text Not Applied/1 - Multi Auto State Text Display Only Applied/2 - Multi Auto State Text Display & Control Applied/3 ? RESERVED
Bit7:(2nd REAR LOCK):0 ? NON REAR LOCK/1 ? REAR LOCK";
