Bit 2~3 RESERVED
Bit 4~5 (2nd Rear Ps Multi Auto Text):0 - Multi Auto State Text Not Applied/1 - Multi Auto State Text Display Only Applied/2 - Multi Auto State Text Display & Control Applied/3 ? RESERVED";
