Bit1 (LCD/NON LCD TYPE): 0- NON LCD/1- LCD TYPE
Bit2~3 (Button Type):0 - HardKey (Push-Return)/1- Touch/2- HardKey + Touch/3 - RESERVED 
Bit4~5 (Button Arragement Type):0 ? Single (Blower-Temp-Mode)/1 ? Single (Temp-Mode-Blower)/2 ? Dual ˇ¤ 3zone ˇ¤ 4zoneˇ¤Etc. /3 - RESERVED 
Bit6~7 (Mode Button):0 ? 1 Button/1 ?  2 Button/2 ? 3 Button";
